                     <interp inst="t18230625-20-off119" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230625-20-off119" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230625-20-cd120" type="crimeDate">17th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-20-off119 t18230625-20-cd120"></join>, a purse, value 1 s.; nine sovereigns, and a half-crown, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230625-20-victim225" type="victimName">
